                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <div class="li-item">
                                    <div class="pic">
                                        <a href="" target="_blank"><img src="~/web_images/product3.png" /></a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="title">
                                        <div>燃煤锅炉</div>
                                        <div>操作简单、触摸屏智能控制、温度压力自动控制、一键启停机操作、火力大小任意控制</div>
